The paper discusses a system for auditing access to personal data, which is relevant to the fields of cybersecurity (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), and privacy (cs.CY). The system also involves statistical analysis and verification, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or software engineering (cs.SE).
